extendedInfo.description: Milky Way Market Game. Maggie has just created the Milky Way Market, the greatest one-stop shop for all your out-of-this world needs! Help Maggie and her little pet  earn enough money to buy a trip to visit Grandpa in the next galaxyClick on the items ordered. Put them in the box. When the box is wrapped, place it on the teleportation device and wait for payment. Reorder items when inventory is low.In Milky Way Market, you have to help Maggie and her alien pal complete food orders at a restaurant in outer space. Once you receive the order, click the corresponding items on he shelves to select them, then place the order in the box. After it is ready for delivery, click the package and place it in the beam platform. Even aliens get hungry!
